short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quick price calculation when booking a car
short.vi: Tính giá nhanh khi đặt xe

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sixt provides car rental services, airport transfers, shuttles to tourist attractions, sightseeing. We have thousands of the best cars from 4 seats to 45 seats, serving all types of customers with travel needs in Vietnam.

To access and calculate the price quickly to know when booking a car more convenient, we have made the Car For Rent sixt application with the following features:
- See the price list for lines from 4, 7, 9, 16, 29, 35 seats
- Calculate price by date, time, airport transfer
Just a few steps to select and enter the data, you have calculated the price.

Contact and application suggestions at:
- Website: https://sixt.vn/
- Address: 260 CauGiay, Hanoi, Vietnam
- Email: Tuyet.sixt@gmail.com
